Package: heteff
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Forest Workflows for Heterogeneous Effect Estimation
Version: 2.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dai", email = "daik54015@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a compact interface around selected generalized random
    forest estimators from the 'grf' package. It focuses on heterogeneous
    treatment effects for observational contrasts, right-censored outcomes,
    and instrumental-variable settings, with simple output tables for ranking
    and interpretation.
